136
00:13:52.546 --> 00:13:54.746
therapies for patients who are needles,

137
00:13:56.226 --> 00:14:00.186
who are really a small number, less than 1%, is with basket

138
00:14:00.206 --> 00:14:03.506
trials. So if you look at NTRK fusion, RET fusion, ALK fusion,

139
00:14:03.646 --> 00:14:07.466
FGFR2 fusion, we've run basket trials of

140
00:14:07.526 --> 00:14:10.946
