00:15:35.566 --> 00:15:39.506
inhibitors, which bound to KRAS off and led

166
00:15:39.566 --> 00:15:43.006
to blockade of downstream signaling. And we did a trial.

167
00:15:43.066 --> 00:15:45.986
Again, we did this basket trial called CRYSTAL-1,

168
00:15:47.286 --> 00:15:49.786
