171
00:15:57.926 --> 00:16:01.786
And if you look at the response rate, it was about 33%.

172
00:16:01.856 --> 00:16:05.386
Now, this was very significant to us because when you look at

173
00:16:05.446 --> 00:16:09.406
chemotherapy in the second-line setting, the response rate is 10 to

174
00:16:09.446 --> 00:16:13.166
15%. That's what we see. But we almost doubled the response rate

