00:17:03.386 --> 00:17:07.046
differently. So if you're KRAS wild type, and if you're

190
00:17:07.126 --> 00:17:10.826
KRAS G12R, you tend to do the best. So your median survival is pushing two

191
00:17:10.886 --> 00:17:14.826
years. D and V is somewhere in the middle, that 12-month survival,

192
00:17:15.206 --> 00:17:18.696
and Q61s tend to do the worst. So there is a prognostic

193
00:17:18.806 --> 00:17:22.146
difference in the way you look at the mutant alleles.

194
00:17:23.247 --> 00:17:26.686
So truly, so that was cracking KRAS, but we are

195
00:17:26.786 --> 00:17:30.766
truly starting the RAS revolution, and we are starting

196
00:17:30.786 --> 00:17:34.326
with this drug called deraxone rasip. So on rasip, right?

197
00:17:34.626 --> 00:17:38.546
Ras on, I-B, on rasip. So deraxone rasip, think

