753
00:50:22.994 --> 00:50:25.864
modification added to hundreds of different proteins,

754
00:50:26.834 --> 00:50:28.614
especially in pancreatic cancer cells.

755
00:50:28.994 --> 00:50:32.694
And so, as I mentioned, it's this Sialyl Lewis a blood group antigen, which is

756
00:50:32.774 --> 00:50:36.514
really what we would call a truncated glycan that leads to a

757
00:50:36.554 --> 00:50:40.304
complete change in its ability to functionally interact with other

758
00:50:40.314 --> 00:50:40.874
proteins.

759
00:50:41.694 --> 00:50:42.554
And so when I was a

760
00:50:44.494 --> 00:50:48.214
postdoctoral fellow, I wanted to study this molecule, one, because I was interested

761
00:50:48.234 --> 00:50:51.594
