00:51:38.703 --> 00:51:42.594
And we have these amazing mouse models that Dave helped develop in Tyler Jack's

776
00:51:42.654 --> 00:51:45.894
lab, where we can induce exactly the same KRAS mutation that's most commonly

777
00:51:45.934 --> 00:51:48.214
