826
00:54:32.634 --> 00:54:36.622
CA19-9.And so I turned to a tool that is clinically

827
00:54:36.682 --> 00:54:40.522
relevant. This is an antibody clone called 5B1 that is highly specific

828
00:54:40.842 --> 00:54:44.802
and has high affinity for CA19-9. This was originally developed by a company

829
00:54:44.902 --> 00:54:47.862
called Madvax, but then was acquired by BioNTech.

830
00:54:48.232 --> 00:54:51.982
And so they have tested this in clinical trials and shown that the CA19-9 blocking

831
00:54:52.042 --> 00:54:55.622
