832
00:54:55.682 --> 00:54:59.362
response rate in the advanced line metastatic setting, and when you combine it with

833
00:54:59.402 --> 00:55:01.722
chemo, had a 27% partial response.

834
00:55:02.542 --> 00:55:06.302
This study was discontinued due to sponsor decision, but we

835
00:55:06.362 --> 00:55:10.322
also learned something really important from this clinical trial, in that

836
00:55:10.382 --> 00:55:14.302
