00:58:37.962 --> 00:58:41.722
In addition, if we block ILIN alpha and TGF beta in the condition

895
00:58:41.782 --> 00:58:45.242
media from these organoids, you can see an impairment in apCAF

896
00:58:45.252 --> 00:58:48.862
differentiation from these pancreatic mesothelial cells.

897
00:58:48.882 --> 00:58:52.842
And so we do think that this is not a novel axis, just one

898
00:58:52.902 --> 00:58:56.722
that is substantially provoked by CA19-9 elevation.

899
00:58:57.662 --> 00:59:01.522
So then we did the in vivo antibody blockade experiment, and then you can again

900
00:59:01.622 --> 00:59:05.101
see that the combined effect of blocking both ILIN alpha and TGF

901
00:59:05.442 --> 00:59:09.182
beta normalize the tissue architecture, decrease collagen

902
00:59:09.202 --> 00:59:13.042
deposition. You get an overall decrease in cancer-associated

903
00:59:13.102 --> 00:59:15.742
fibroblasts, and these are primarily in the antigen-presenting

904
00:59:16.782 --> 00:59:19.032
compartment, as well as a decrease in Tregs.

905
00:59:19.102 --> 00:59:22.992
Now, you'll notice that with ILIN alpha blocking antibody by itself, you also

906
00:59:23.022 --> 00:59:26.622
impair Treg differentiation. This is a little bit difficult to dissect because

907
00:59:26.642 --> 00:59:30.502
these are important for both apCAF differentiation as well as Treg

