01:05:42.558 --> 01:05:46.387
infrastructure. I also had a ton of help with a lot of the bioinformatic

1013
01:05:46.438 --> 01:05:49.108
analysis from Tag Yu as well as Jonathan.

1014
01:05:50.038 --> 01:05:53.528
And then my immunology partners in crime, because I didn't start off as a

1015
01:05:53.538 --> 01:05:57.078
glycobiologist, let alone an immunologist, are Ye Zheng and Sue

