01:05:57.098 --> 01:06:00.688
Kag. And then, of course, my most

1017
01:06:00.718 --> 01:06:04.678
fun scientific experiment is my son, Oliver, who is now

1018
01:06:04.718 --> 01:06:08.608
three years old. So he has been my fearless cheerleader through all of this

1019
01:06:08.638 --> 01:06:08.908
work.

1020
01:06:09.798 --> 01:06:12.038
Thank you so much. I'd be happy to take questions.

1021
01:06:15.378 --> 01:06:19.238
Thank you. I know the deans of the pancreas

1022
01:06:19.318 --> 01:06:23.138
tumor microenvironment are sitting in the audience, so we'll defer questions to the

1023
01:06:23.198 --> 01:06:26.718
