01:13:09.330 --> 01:13:13.150
from NYU by one of our medical students at this ACR.

1137
01:13:13.650 --> 01:13:17.330
Diabetes is always one of the features that rises to the top.

1138
01:13:17.730 --> 01:13:21.150
So this is something that is clearly present in the

1139
01:13:21.230 --> 01:13:25.150
context of a risk factor or a harbinger

1140
01:13:25.250 --> 01:13:29.010
of pancreas cancer. And in fact, even

1141
01:13:29.050 --> 01:13:32.410
patients who have precancerous lesions like these IPMNs, when their

1142
01:13:32.550 --> 01:13:36.310
IPMN progresses to an invasive cancer, this is work from

